# INInteractionDirection.incoming

**Case**

An interaction in which information is received on the device.

## Declaration

```swift
case incoming
```

## Discussion

Choose this value when the interaction involves a message sent to the user of the device.

## Constants

- **INInteractionDirection.unspecified**: An unspecified direction.
- **INInteractionDirection.outgoing**: An interaction in which information is sent from the device.
